commit.message:
v0.014

          - Always return an empty file as an empty string

Always return an empty file as an empty string

Previously it could return an empty list instead in list context.

v0.013

          Always split on newlines in read_lines
Eliminate unused variable from test

Always split on newlines in read_lines

Previously its behavior would depend on the value of $/

v0.012

          Depend on Encode 2.11 for STOP_AT_PARTIAL

Depend on Encode 2.11 for STOP_AT_PARTIAL

Without this, one can get failures on 5.8.7 and lower unless Encode
happens to have been upgraded already.

v0.011

          Correctly set value of $PerlIO::encoding::fallback
          Don't skip latin-1 checking
Expand dzil bundle

Don't skip latin-1 checking

:raw and :encoding(latin-1) are identical when the data is valid, but
not when it isn't. Hence this optimization shouldn't happen.

Add STOP_AT_PARTIAL to $PerlIO::encoding::fallback

Otherwise, characters overlapping buffer boundaries would cause failues

v0.010

          Recognize "latin-1" as iso-8859-1

Recognize "latin-1" as iso-8859-1

This happens to fix a bug in write_binary that caused it to do a iso-8859
encode instead of doing proper binary.
Improve documentation

v0.009

          Load PerlIO::encoding before localizing $PerlIO::encoding::fallback

Load PerlIO::encoding before localizing $fallback

fixes https://rt.cpan.org/Ticket/Display.html?id=116738
cf. https://rt.perl.org/Public/Bug/Display.html?id=127149

Check encode related warnings after read_text

Add a unittest to check whether calling read_text results in warnings when
later writing in utf8 encoding

v0.008

          Impose scalar context on do/eval/require

Impose scalar context on do/eval/require

Without it, when the do/eval/require fails it returns an empty list,
which gives us:

    Odd number of elements in anonymous hash at .../File/Slurper.pm line 32.

Scalar context makes it return undef.

POD fix

Fix typo in POD.

v0.007

          Added more items to a SEE ALSO
          Fixed up benchmarks
Fixed up benchmarks
Added more items to a SEE ALSO

v0.006

          Unmark experimental status
          Always croak on encoding error
Various minor documentation improvements
Always croak on encoding error
Unmark experimental status

v0.005

          Get rid of singular named options
Make read_lines arguments positional too
Get rid of singular named options
